 194:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *            - All interrupts disabled
 195:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @note   This function doesn't modify the configuration of the
